Third Department,

August, 1966

(August 1, 1966) In the Matter of Peter J. Fiorella, Jr., Doing Business as Town and Country Club, Appellant, v. Donald S. Hostetter et al., Constituting the State Liquor Authority, Respondents.

Motion for modification of decision [25 A D 2d 801] dated April 29, 1966 denied, without costs. Gibson, P. J., Herlihy, Reynolds, Taylor and Aulisi, JJ., concur.
